 next steps after the session. Best when messaging emphasizes momentum, application, or moving from insight into action.', 'Avoid when the card is mainly about understanding core concepts or building team-wide alignment, where the clarity or alignment variants are more suitable.', 'https://tiuljkhdhhmvscujnslz.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/campaign-assets/benefits/momentum.png', null, null, ARRAY['hybrid_content_section'], ARRAY['artificial intelligence','innovation','implementation','business transformation'], ARRAY['Corporate Leadership','IT Companies','Associations','Operations Teams'], ARRAY['Keynote','Workshop','Seminar','Conference'], ARRAY['action','implementation','momentum','next steps'], true, 72, '2026-04-23 06:15:40.54407+00', '2026-04-23 06:15:40.54407+00');